DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><strong><code>USVString</code></strong> 对应 unicode 标量值的所有可能序列的集合。在 JavaScript 中返回时， <code>USVString</code> 映射到 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>String</code></a> 。它通常仅用于执行文本处理的 API，需要一串 unicode 标量值才能进行操作。除了不允许不成对的代理代码之外， <code>USVString</code> 等同于 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> 。 <code>USVString</code> 中存在的不成对的代理代码由浏览器转换为 Unicode '替换字符' <code>U+FFFD</code>, (�).</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>译注：</p>\n\n<p>Unicode 标量值（ Unicode scalar values ）：字符的代号。</p>\n\n<p>不成对的代理代码（ Unpaired surrogate codepoints ）：高代理代码后面没有低代理代码，或者低代理代码之前没有高代理代码。</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://heycam.github.io/webidl/#idl-USVString\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web IDL<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">USVString</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Candidate Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另见","title":"另见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>String</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>CSSOMString</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/btoa\">Binary strings</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"另见","id":"另见"}],"summary":"USVString 对应 unicode 标量值的所有可能序列的集合。在 JavaScript 中返回时， USVString 映射到 String 。它通常仅用于执行文本处理的 API，需要一串 unicode 标量值才能进行操作。除了不允许不成对的代理代码之外， USVString 等同于 DOMString 。 USVString 中存在的不成对的代理代码由浏览器转换为 Unicode '替换字符' U+FFFD, (�).","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"USVString","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"USVString","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"USVString","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/conflicting/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/string_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/conflicting/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/string_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"uneval()"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb","title":"USVString"}],"pageTitle":"USVString | MDN","noIndexing":true}}